Gnome virtual filessystem
gvfs-mount sftp||ftp||smb.. to mount to
$HOME/.gvfs

Users and stuff (some specific to ubuntu instances on ec2)
sudo passwd ubuntu #set the defaults users password
man sudo_port	# good manual about users and rights 
				# etc on the ec2 ubuntu instance
sudo adduser <user> admin # the admin group has lots of privilegies
visudo # change which users/groups that have sudo rights
$HOME/.ssh/autheti..keys.. # which keys should have access to the machine
